headline: Morgan Stanley issues shock take on the stock market

headline: OPEC+ Blinks, Trump Threatens Nigeria, and Oil Markets Start to Crack
summary: A supply pause, drone strikes, and geopolitical flare-ups are colliding to reshape oil's next big move.

headline: Earnings Growth Will Be Better Than Expected, Morgan Stanley's Wilson Says
summary: Morgan Stanley Chief US Equity Strategist Mike Wilson says earnings growth will be better than expected next year and the US economy is still in a rolling recovery. Wilson also says interest rates are too high. He speaks on "Bloomberg Surveillance."
